SONiC Data Directory
====================

This directory contains SONiC runtime data and configuration.

Files
-----

sonic-image.tar.gz
  Compressed podman archive containing the SONiC container image.
  Loaded by sonic-import.service on first boot.

sonic-version.txt
  Version identifier for the SONiC image.

.image-imported
  Marker file created after successful image import.
  Prevents re-importing on subsequent boots.

config_db.json
  SONiC configuration file, mounted into the container at /etc/sonic/config_db.json.
  Created by start-sonic script from /etc/hotstack-sonic/config_db.json or defaults.
